    "description": "All automated metrics were scored by Claude Sonnet 4.5 (Anthropic). To test whether findings depend on a single evaluator's idiosyncrasies, all 204 outputs were re-scored with ChatGPT-4o (OpenAI) using identical prompts and rubrics.",
